<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-3168] Enable Throttling only during nightly builds</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-3168</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Some of my tests take forever even on a big &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/smile.gif&quot; height=&quot;20&quot; width=&quot;20&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt; machine. In order to speed up our tests we should default the IO throttling to NEVER and only run in during nightly.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
